text: Nice food variety and drinks offered. The live band that night is super engaging and the audience are engaging too.

Nice pool table which is free.
Only ate a couple appetizers, but they were very good. The mini sliders were great!

Had the steak and it was flawless. My children are enjoying themselves, playing the arcade console, darts and the mini pool table while the adults are busy singing karaoke! They also have a good range of alcohol as well with nice promos for the beer towers!
Very nice environment! We had happy hour 1-for-1 tower and yummy food!
Awesome food and vibes. Love their liveband performances. Definitely a great place to chill any day!
